PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784742505
OL,3,CChina 'strongly dissatisfied'
OL,4,Cfollowing decision to nationalise
OL,5,CBritish Steel
OL,7,FChina's government says it is
OL,8,F"strongly dissatisfied" with the
OL,9,Fdecision to nationalise British Steel.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, British Steel was brought
OL,12,Funder public ownership to protect "the
OL,13,Ffuture of steel production", the UK
OL,14,FGovernment announced.
OL,16,FThe Department for Business and Trade
OL,17,Fsaid the move was essential to
OL,18,Fmaintain steel production at the
OL,19,Fcompany's site in Scunthorpe,
OL,20,FLincolnshire, to protect its future
OL,21,Fand UK supply chains.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@WO]tD@cOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
