OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784742505
OL,3,CChina 'strongly dissatisfied'
OL,4,Cfollowing decision to nationalise
OL,5,CBritish Steel
OL,7,FThe move will also help protect jobs
OL,8,Fof hundreds of people on Teesside
OL,9,Fwhere the company operates two long
OL,10,Fproduct mills in Redcar and at
OL,11,FSkinningrove in East Cleveland.
OL,13,FHowever, China's Ministry of Commerce
OL,14,F(Mofcom) said the move dealt "a severe
OL,15,Fblow to Chinese companies' confidence
OL,16,Fin investing in the UK".
OL,18,FBritish Steel was previously owned by
OL,19,Fthe Chinese company Jingye.
OL,26,@vD@^OUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784742505
OL,3,CChina 'strongly dissatisfied'
OL,4,Cfollowing decision to nationalise
OL,5,CBritish Steel
OL,7,FThe company had previously planned to
OL,8,Fclose its Scunthorpe blast furnaces in
OL,9,FNorth Lincolnshire.
OL,11,FBut Parliament was recalled on a
OL,12,FSaturday in April last year to approve
OL,13,Fspecial measures legislation to keep
OL,14,Fthe plant open.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784742505
OL,3,CChina 'strongly dissatisfied'
OL,4,Cfollowing decision to nationalise
OL,5,CBritish Steel
OL,7,FA Mofcom spokesperson told Chinese
OL,8,Fmedia outlet The Global Times: "The UK
OL,9,Fside, disregarding Jingye Group's
OL,10,Fimportant contributions to the British
OL,11,Feconomy and society, forcibly took
OL,12,Fcontrol of British Steel and
OL,13,Fsubsequently nationalised the company
OL,14,Fin the name of national security,
OL,15,Fseriously undermining Jingye's
OL,16,Flegitimate rights and interests and
OL,17,Fdealing a severe blow to Chinese
OL,18,Fcompanies' confidence in investing in
OL,19,Fthe UK.
OL,26,@pD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784742505
OL,3,CChina 'strongly dissatisfied'
OL,4,Cfollowing decision to nationalise
OL,5,CBritish Steel
OL,7,F"China firmly opposes and is strongly
OL,8,Fdissatisfied with the UK government's
OL,9,Fdecision.
OL,11,F"China will closely follow
OL,12,Fdevelopments, support Chinese
OL,13,Fcompanies in safeguarding their rights
OL,14,Fthrough legal means, and take strong
OL,15,Fmeasures to firmly protect the
OL,16,Finterests of Chinese companies."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
