OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784742505
OL,3,CChina 'strongly dissatisfied'
OL,4,Cfollowing decision to nationalise
OL,5,CBritish Steel
OL,7,FThe spokesperson reportedly said the
OL,8,FUK Government should "abide by
OL,9,Frelevant international rules,
OL,10,Fearnestly fulfil its obligations under
OL,11,Fthe China-UK bilateral investment
OL,12,Ftreaty, treat Chinese companies
OL,13,Foperating in the UK in a fair and
OL,14,Fimpartial manner, and fully protect
OL,15,Ftheir legitimate rights and interests".
OL,26,@pD@VOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
