OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784742505
OL,3,CChina 'strongly dissatisfied'
OL,4,Cfollowing decision to nationalise
OL,5,CBritish Steel
OL,7,FFollowing Thursday's nationalisation,
OL,8,Fa new leadership team was appointed to
OL,9,Ffocus on stabilising the business and
OL,10,Fturning it into a "commercially
OL,11,Fsustainable, low-carbon enterprise",
OL,12,Fthe UK Government said.
OL,14,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,15,Fon Thursday: "British Steel is part of
OL,16,Fthe fabric of our nation and a
OL,17,Fcornerstone of Britain's industrial
OL,18,Fstrength.
OL,26,@rD@SOUsD@cO]wD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784742505
OL,3,CChina 'strongly dissatisfied'
OL,4,Cfollowing decision to nationalise
OL,5,CBritish Steel
OL,7,F"Today's decision secures the future
OL,8,Fof steelmaking in the UK, protects
OL,9,Fskilled jobs and safeguards a vital
OL,10,Fnational capability.
OL,12,F"This Government will always act in
OL,13,Fthe national interest to support
OL,14,FBritish industry, strengthen our
OL,15,Feconomy and ensure the industries we
OL,16,Frely on can thrive long into the
OL,17,Ffuture."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
