PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1784742505
OL,3,CChina 'strongly dissatisfied'
OL,4,Cfollowing decision to nationalise
OL,5,CBritish Steel
OL,7,FThe announcement followed the Steel
OL,8,FIndustry (Nationalisation) Act 2026
OL,9,Freceiving royal assent and becoming
OL,10,Flaw. The new law allows ministers to
OL,11,Ftransfer steel businesses' shares or
OL,12,Fproperty into public ownership.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/9
